skdetail:

Invocation Name: swift meditate
des:
Swift meditate is a series of quick meditation routines that Alexa will guide you through. Alexa doesn't have the calmest of voices but using these methods as a baseline for your own meditation will help you along the right path. 

Alexa will break the meditation into bite sized chunks so you can stop when you are ready. Simply say 'Continue' to proceed to the next part of the meditation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
